{
  "texts": [
    "We asked the LLM to determine the relevance of the paper, its field, the paradigm of the interpretability method, the mechanism being explained, the scope and accessibility of the method, and whether it is causalbased.",
    "Additionally, we asked the LLM to write a one-sentence summary of the paper and explain its paradigm annotation.",
    "The LLM was also instructed to explicitly extract the names of the interpretability methods employed in the paper.",
    "We generated three responses (in a JSON format with LLM annotations) for each paper and determined the final annotation of each question by the majority vote.",
    "After relevancy filtering, 2,009 papers remained."
  ]
}